          "notes": [
            "新增 Codex 待授權 OAuth 帳號卡片，帳號備註可先儲存，後續從同一張卡片繼續完成授權。"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "version": "1.0.3",
      "date": "2026-07-04",
      "notes": [
        "Improved Codex platform adapter coverage for API service, batch delete, session transfer, model provider usage, and request log repricing flows.",
        "Fixed Codex local API service and image generation settings to keep saved runtime options stable across reloads."
      ],
      "locales": {
        "zh-CN": {
          "notes": [
            "补齐 Codex 平台 adapter 对 API 服务、批量删除、会话迁移、模型供应商用量和请求日志重算费用等流程的支持。",
            "修复 Codex 本地 API 服务和 image_generation 设置，保存后的运行选项在刷新或重启后保持稳定。"
          ]
        },
        "zh-TW": {
          "notes": [
            "補齊 Codex 平台 adapter 對 API 服務、批量刪除、會話遷移、模型供應商用量與請求日誌重算費用等流程的支援。",
            "修復 Codex 本機 API 服務與 image_generation 設定，儲存後的執行選項在重新整理或重啟後保持穩定。"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "version": "1.0.2",
      "date": "2026-07-03",
      "notes": [
        "Improved Codex account persistence, local API service compatibility, session transfer, batch operations, and sensitive account notes support."
      ],
      "locales": {
        "zh-CN": {
          "notes": [
            "改进 Codex 账号持久化、本地 API 服务兼容性、会话迁移、批量操作和账号敏感备注支持。"
          ]
        },
        "zh-TW": {
          "notes": [
            "改進 Codex 帳號持久化、本機 API 服務相容性、會話遷移、批量操作與帳號敏感備註支援。"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "version": "1.0.1",
      "date": "2026-07-02",
      "notes": [
        "Removed Codex quota auto-refresh from settings.",
        "Changed Codex current-account refresh to work independently without relying on quota auto-refresh.",
        "Changed Codex refresh behavior to avoid default full-account quota scans; authorization keep-alive now only renews due tokens.",
        "Moved Codex-specific settings to the Codex settings popover, with General settings opening the Codex settings entry.",
        "Changed platform package replacement to uninstall the old package before installing the downloaded package."
      ],
      "locales": {
        "zh-CN": {
          "notes": [
            "Codex 设置去掉配额自动刷新。",
            "Codex 当前账号刷新改为独立生效，不再依赖配额自动刷新。",
            "Codex 刷新逻辑改为不默认全量扫描账号配额；账号授权保活只续期到期 token。",
            "Codex 专属设置迁移到 Codex 设置弹框，通用设置只保留跳转入口。",
            "平台包替换改为先卸载旧包，再安装已下载的新包。"
          ]
        },
        "zh-TW": {
          "notes": [
            "Codex 設定移除配額自動刷新。",
            "Codex 目前帳號刷新改為獨立生效，不再依賴配額自動刷新。",
            "Codex 刷新邏輯改為不預設全量掃描帳號配額；帳號授權保活只續期到期 token。",
            "Codex 專屬設定遷移到 Codex 設定彈框，通用設定只保留跳轉入口。",
            "平台包替換改為先解除安裝舊包，再安裝已下載的新包。"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "date": "2026-07-01",
      "notes": [
        "Platform has been split into an independent package and now runs independently from the host application."
      ],
      "locales": {
        "zh-CN": {
          "notes": [
            "平台拆成独立的包独立运行。"
          ]
        },
        "zh-TW": {
          "notes": [
            "平台拆成獨立的包並獨立運行。"
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ],
